- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and speech analysis for emotion recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new method of learning using convolutional attention networks. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech data. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is another possible category as the paper deals with multi-modal emotion recognition from vision and speech. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with machine learning techniques for emotion recognition.
